overview:
A Marketplace for Commercial Real Estate.

We started SpaceList to make it easy for people to find the perfect office, retail or warehouse space. We’re doing it by bringing all of Canada’s commercial real estate listings together in one place. No other website lets you cover so much of the market so quickly.

Our goal is to make it dramatically easier for people to find and market office, retail and industrial space. We are working closely with the biggest firms in the business to make commercial real estate more accessible and improve the efficiency of the market. As part of that objective, we will never charge you a fee to search for space.
